column_1": "<p><strong>Gold & Pearl Pieces:</strong> Put jewelry on last, take it off first. Wipe with a soft cloth after wearing. Store in the provided pouch. Avoid perfume, chlorine, and harsh chemicals. Pearls love being worn \u2014 natural skin oils maintain their luster.</p><p><strong>Enamel Rings:</strong> Avoid hard impact. Remove for heavy work. Clean with a soft damp cloth. Never use ultrasonic cleaners on enamel.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 700, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "two_column_tab_QmTHWe": {"type": "two_column_tab", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Shipping & Returns", "content_vertical_alignment": "top", "column_spacing": 48, "heading_column_1": "Made to Order", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p>Every piece is handcrafted to order in NYC. Production takes 4\u20138 weeks. You'll receive email updates during production and tracking when it ships. All orders ship fully insured with signature required.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text", "heading_column_2": "Returns & Warranty", "heading_font_class_column_2": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_2": "h3", "text_column_2": "<p>All sales are final \u2014 each piece is made specifically for you. 1-year warranty covers manufacturing defects. If your piece arrives damaged, contact us within 14 days with photos.</p>", "page_for_content_column_2": "", "custom_liquid_column_2": "", "text_font_class_column_2": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_2": 100, "image_position_column_2": "above_text"}}}, "block_order": ["product_description_B47rUG", "one_column_UfpW9X", "one_column_8gLpCt", "two_column_tab_QmTHWe"], "settings": {"tab_ali